snippet.title: Visual Novel - Lighthouse of guiding flames
snippet.description:
Ethani lost her way and ended up at the lighthouse. Where did she come from and where should she go? Explore a mystery Visual Novel to reveal the past and set sail once more...

VN: drama, mystery, fantasy
Developer: TomoToro
More info: twitter.com/9narrative
